text:
Positive:  The food was prepared quickly.  We ordered the food over the phone and it was ready in 15 minutes.

Negatives:  It is not cheap.  I like a bit more wasabi and ginger and it was all an extra charge.  There was not very much included with our dinner.  

Ordered <Miso soup> and it was in a large container, but was shocked to see that it was a quarter full.  I was really disappointed and felt a little cheated.
